## 4. Frontend — Admin: Exam Enrollment Page

**Create:** `src/app/admin/exam/enrollment/page.tsx`

Layout: `"use client"`, `<main className="min-h-screen bg-[#0D0A1A] text-white p-8">`

### Sections:
1. **Header** — icon badge (ClipboardList) + title "Exam Enrollment" + subtitle
2. **Exam Selector** — dropdown to select an exam
3. **Enrollment Table** — shows enrolled students for selected exam (name, roll, status, enrolled_at)
4. **Generate Hall Tickets** button — calls POST `/core/hall-tickets/generate`
5. **Hall Tickets List** — shows generated tickets with ticket number, room, seat, download button

### Data Fetching:
- `apiGet('campusCore/exams')` — list exams
- `apiGet('campusCore/exams/:id/enrollments')` — enrollment list
- `apiPost('campusCore/hall-tickets/generate', { exam_id })` — generate tickets
- `apiGet('campusCore/hall-tickets/my')` — not needed on admin page

